channel.title: Problem
channel.description:

ALSO: [size=18pt]PEOPLE SAY THAT YOUR IP MIGHT HAVE CHANGED AND U HAVE TO PORTFORWARD AGAIN, IT HAS NOT CHANGED AND EVERYTHING SAYS MY SERVER IS ONLINE...
IF U HAVE SKYPE OR TEAMVEIWER I WILL LOVE YOU TO HELP ME![/size]
